segment.source: Microsoft Diagnostics and Recovery Toolset (DaRT) 10 provides the following listed set of Windows PowerShell cmdlets.
segment.target: Microsoft Diagnostics and Recovery Toolset (DaRT) 10 provides the following listed set of Windows PowerShell cmdlets.

segment.source: Administrators can use these PowerShell cmdlets to perform various DaRT 10 server tasks from the command prompt rather than from the DaRT Recovery Image wizard.
segment.target: Administrators can use these PowerShell cmdlets to perform various DaRT 10 server tasks from the command prompt rather than from the DaRT Recovery Image wizard.
